  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p style="margin: 0px 0px 11px;">Buffet breakfast is served from 7.30am to 10.30am. You can enjoy fresh, local foods like bruschetta, local cheeses and homemade cakes. A half board upgrade is also available.</p>
<p style="margin: 0px 0px 11px;"><strong>Lampolla Restaurant</strong> has a cosy, informal atmosphere and large windows so you can enjoy the views as you dine. They have lots of Tuscan food on the menu and a great wine list with local labels. The restaurant is open for lunch from 12.30pm to 3pm and for dinner from 7.30pm to 10pm.</p>
<p><strong>Loliva Bistrot</strong> is open every day from 12pm to midnight so pull up a chair and order your favourite drink whenever you want. They serves snacks throughout the day too.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
