  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Pool</strong></span></p>
<p>The outdoor is open from May to September and has a poolside snack bar serving drinks and light lunches.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Spa</strong></span></p>
<p>The impressive 1,000<span>m²</span> spa has a heated indoor pool with hydro-massage jets, an outdoor relaxation area, sauna, turkish bath and sensory showers. A three hour wellness package is included for all Inghams guests aged 12+, along with bathrobes, towels and slippers. You can then book additional wellness packages, treatments and massages in resort (payable locally).</p>
<p><span>Opening times: 10am - 8pm and until midnight on </span>Thursdays</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities </strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Free onsite parking</li>
<li>Free WiFi</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
