  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p style="margin: 0px 0px 11px;"><span>Villasanpaolo Spa Hotel is the perfect choice for a relaxing stay in the middle of the Tuscan Countryside. It's </span>just two miles from San Gimignano and it has amazing views over the town's towers and surrounding countryside. There's an idyllic outdoor pool in the gardens and an impressive hydro-massage pool in the spa. We love the food here - it's all locally-sourced and every bite is delicious.</p>]]></listingDescription>
