  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Rooms </strong>measure 18-22m<sup>2 </sup>and have been finished in a tasteful Tuscan style. Some overlook the garden while others enjoy views over vineyards towards San Gimignano. These rooms sleep up to three people. They have air conditioning and free WiFi. All rooms have an outside space, patio or terrace. </p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms </strong>offer more space with 26m<sup>2</sup> and are ideal for families. These rooms sleep up to three people and have a patio or terrace. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
